d leaves the reader almost breathless. I am trying to avoid telling much of the plot, as much of the power of the novel lies in opening yourself up to being surprised, wanting to hear characters' secrets and dreading them at the same time. Marías also develops different threads of the novel that all come together eerily in the last two chapters, leaving us with a dread of the cyclical nature of human experience, the repetition in human relationships, and the fear that sins carry over from one generation to the next. ","rating":5,"shelving":{"__typename":"Shelving","shelf":{"__typename":"Shelf","name":"read","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/5974610?shelf=read"},"taggings":[{"__typename":"Tagging","tag":{"__typename":"Tag","name":"spain","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/5974610?shelf=spain"}}],"webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/340798822"},"likeCount":80,"viewerHasLiked":null,"commentCount":10,"viewerCanComment({\"resourceType\":\"review\"})":null},"Book:kca://book/amzn1.gr.book.v1.spCT2Cy4AieACEWqDUsVyA":{"id":"kca://book/amzn1.gr.book.v1.spCT2Cy4AieACEWqDUsVyA","__typename":"Book"},"User:11592808":{"id":11592808,"__typename":"User","legacyId":11592808,"imageUrlSquare":"https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1373322264i/11592808._UX200_CR0,49,200,200_.jpg","isAuthor":false,"textReviewsCount":935,"viewableName":"Sawsan","isBlockedByViewer":false,"webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/user/show/11592808-sawsan","contributor":null,"isFollowing":false,"isFriend":false,"followersCount":1133},"Review:kca://review:goodreads/amzn1.gr.review:goodreads.v1.2lIJSA2R1Frj0QLWRxrmBQ":{"id":"kca://review:goodreads/amzn1.gr.review:goodreads.v1.2lIJSA2R1Frj0QLWRxrmBQ","__typename":"Review","book":{"__ref":"Book:kca://book/amzn1.gr.book.v1.spCT2Cy4AieACEWqDUsVyA"},"creator":{"__ref":"User:11592808"},"recommendFor":null,"updatedAt":1643533609169,"createdAt":1587852536183,"spoilerStatus":false,"lastRevisionAt":1643493